translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 昨日は夜遅くまでエッチしていた感じ（どうとでも取れる感じで）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It felt like we were having sex until late last night (could be interpreted any way).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルの入れさせたコーヒーを飲みながら、いい調子だ。勝てる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Drinking the coffee Syyl made me have, I'm in good shape. I can win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: と司令部に入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I entered the headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セシル、コパンドン、篠田、司令部はもう大忙し・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cecil, Kopandon, Shinoda, the headquarters is already very busy...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、始まりました、両軍の先鋒が接触しました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has just begun, the vanguards of both armies have made contact.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物大将軍か魔人が出るまで待つつもりだったが、戦いたい気分だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was planning to wait until the demon general or the demon appears, but I feel like fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺も出るぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm going out too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、人類側の陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the human side's position.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦場の様子、開戦から１時間が過ぎた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation on the battlefield, one hour has passed since the start of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 篠田勘助が指揮している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kansuke Shinoda is commanding.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 両軍５割ほどの部隊が戦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: About half of the troops from both sides are fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 誰かが聞く、一気に全軍突撃させては・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone asks, 'Why don't we order the entire army to charge at once...?'.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは愚策、戦局を見ながらタイミングより新戦力を投入する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's a foolish plan. We introduce new forces at the right timing while watching the battle situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 兵士は疲れる者、新しい兵力は突進力がある
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Soldiers get tired; new troops have the power to charge aggressively.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦のうんちくいろいろ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Various tactical theories and details.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よし、マリア殿に連絡、チューリップ３号Ｈ型を前へ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, contact Lady Maria, send the Tulip No.3 H-type forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この地点の敵軍を分断するぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We will split the enemy forces at this point.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類側が押している様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems the human side is pressing forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、戦場の中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the battlefield.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チューリップ部隊の猛攻
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Tulip unit's fierce attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、戦場の中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the battlefield.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイの活躍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The exploits of the demon Ray.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦場でのランス達、もうかなりの敵部隊を撃破した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and his group on the battlefield have already defeated quite a few enemy units.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 絶好調である、魔物将軍の部隊を発見した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They're in top form; they have located the demon general's unit.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちっ、魔物大将軍では無いのか、だが、敵の中枢だ、ぶっころす
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tch, it's not the demon great general, but it's the enemy's core. I'll kill them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いくぞー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、人類側司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the human side's headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 開戦から２時間が過ぎた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two hours have passed since the start of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦を指示している篠田勘助。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kansuke Shinoda is giving operational orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、チューリップなど主力は魔人レイと当たらないようにしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The main forces like Lance and Tulip are avoiding contact with the demon Ray.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイはこちらの消耗部隊で動きを止め、こちらの主力は敵中核を確実に削る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Ray uses our worn-out units to stop their movement, while our main force steadily cuts down the enemy core.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うまい作戦である
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It is a clever strategy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勝っている、このまま押し切れるはずである・・が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We are winning and should be able to push through like this... but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何故、ジフテリア軍は動かぬ。突撃依頼は出したはずだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why is the Diphtheria army not moving? The charge orders should have been given.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、再度出したのですが、もう少し準備がかかるとかなんとかで引き延ばされて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, the order was sent again, but they delayed it saying they need a little more preparation or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どういう事だ、まさか・・ジフテリア軍が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What is this? No way... The Diphtheria army is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ジフテリア軍の陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Diphtheria army's camp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指令部から来た使者をうまく引き替えさせる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They skillfully turn away the messenger sent from the headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 副官が、何故動かないのですか、我々が今動けば勝ちは確実です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The deputy officer says, "Why aren't we moving? If we move now, victory is certain."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この戦いは自由都市地域全体のいえ人類の命運に左右する一大決戦です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This battle is a major decisive battle that will determine the fate of the entire Free City region, indeed humanity's fate.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けると滅びてしまうかもしれないのですぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If we lose, we might perish.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （そうだ・・この戦いの結果で我々は全員死ぬかもしれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (That's right... depending on the outcome of this battle, we might all die.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だからこそ、私は都市長としてジフテリアを守らねばいけないのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's why, as the city mayor, I must protect Diphtheria.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たとえ、他国を犠牲にしようと）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if it means sacrificing other nations.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 回想
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Flashback.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コンバート、カチューシャとの密談
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A secret meeting between Convert and Katyusha.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 決戦時に裏切る事でその後、ジフテリアの安全は保証する約束
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A promise guaranteeing Diphtheria's safety after betrayal at the decisive battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 悪いが裏切らせてもらう、頃合いだな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry, but I have to betray you. The time has come.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 副官に指示する、攻撃開始だ、ただ、目標は魔軍では無い、近くのＸＸＸ軍（布陣図見てから決める）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He orders the deputy officer, 'Start the attack. However, the target is not the demon army, but the nearby XXX army (decided after viewing the deployment map).'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんですってと副官が驚くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The deputy officer is surprised, saying, 'What did you say?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 別の副官が止める、都市長閣下も苦渋の決断なのだと、お前も軍人なら従え
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Another deputy officer stops him, saying, 'The city mayor is making a painful decision. If you are a soldier, obey.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・わかりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Understood.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこにランスからの手紙が届く、受け取るビョンホウ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, a letter from Lance arrives; Byonhou receives it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを見て真っ青になる、ま、待て裏切り中止
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing it, he turns pale. 'W-wait, cancel the betrayal!'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すぐに魔軍に向けて進撃せよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Advance immediately towards the demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon army headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦通りにならずに驚く、大将軍ピサロ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Great General Pizarro is surprised that the plan is not going as expected.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 昨日は夜遅くまでエッチしていた感じ（どうとでも取れる感じで）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It felt like we were having sex until late last night (could be interpreted any way).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルの入れさせたコーヒーを飲みながら、いい調子だ。勝てる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Drinking the coffee Syyl made me have, I'm in good shape. I can win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: と司令部に入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I entered the headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セシル、コパンドン、篠田、司令部はもう大忙し・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cecil, Kopandon, Shinoda, the headquarters is already very busy...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、始まりました、両軍の先鋒が接触しました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has just begun, the vanguards of both armies have made contact.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物大将軍か魔人が出るまで待つつもりだったが、戦いたい気分だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was planning to wait until the demon general or the demon appears, but I feel like fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺も出るぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm going out too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、人類側の陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the human side's position.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦場の様子、開戦から１時間が過ぎた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation on the battlefield, one hour has passed since the start of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 篠田勘助が指揮している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kansuke Shinoda is commanding.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 両軍５割ほどの部隊が戦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: About half of the troops from both sides are fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 誰かが聞く、一気に全軍突撃させては・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Someone asks, 'Why don't we order the entire army to charge at once...?'.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは愚策、戦局を見ながらタイミングより新戦力を投入する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's a foolish plan. We introduce new forces at the right timing while watching the battle situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 兵士は疲れる者、新しい兵力は突進力がある
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Soldiers get tired; new troops have the power to charge aggressively.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦のうんちくいろいろ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Various tactical theories and details.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よし、マリア殿に連絡、チューリップ３号Ｈ型を前へ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, contact Lady Maria, send the Tulip No.3 H-type forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この地点の敵軍を分断するぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We will split the enemy forces at this point.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類側が押している様子
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems the human side is pressing forward.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、戦場の中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the battlefield.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: チューリップ部隊の猛攻
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Tulip unit's fierce attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、戦場の中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, in the battlefield.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイの活躍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The exploits of the demon Ray.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦場でのランス達、もうかなりの敵部隊を撃破した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and his group on the battlefield have already defeated quite a few enemy units.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 絶好調である、魔物将軍の部隊を発見した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They're in top form; they have located the demon general's unit.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちっ、魔物大将軍では無いのか、だが、敵の中枢だ、ぶっころす
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tch, it's not the demon great general, but it's the enemy's core. I'll kill them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いくぞー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、人類側司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the human side's headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 開戦から２時間が過ぎた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two hours have passed since the start of the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦を指示している篠田勘助。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kansuke Shinoda is giving operational orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、チューリップなど主力は魔人レイと当たらないようにしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The main forces like Lance and Tulip are avoiding contact with the demon Ray.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイはこちらの消耗部隊で動きを止め、こちらの主力は敵中核を確実に削る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Ray uses our worn-out units to stop their movement, while our main force steadily cuts down the enemy core.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うまい作戦である
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It is a clever strategy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勝っている、このまま押し切れるはずである・・が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We are winning and should be able to push through like this... but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何故、ジフテリア軍は動かぬ。突撃依頼は出したはずだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why is the Diphtheria army not moving? The charge orders should have been given.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、再度出したのですが、もう少し準備がかかるとかなんとかで引き延ばされて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, the order was sent again, but they delayed it saying they need a little more preparation or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どういう事だ、まさか・・ジフテリア軍が・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What is this? No way... The Diphtheria army is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ジフテリア軍の陣地
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Diphtheria army's camp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指令部から来た使者をうまく引き替えさせる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They skillfully turn away the messenger sent from the headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 副官が、何故動かないのですか、我々が今動けば勝ちは確実です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The deputy officer says, "Why aren't we moving? If we move now, victory is certain."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この戦いは自由都市地域全体のいえ人類の命運に左右する一大決戦です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This battle is a major decisive battle that will determine the fate of the entire Free City region, indeed humanity's fate.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けると滅びてしまうかもしれないのですぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If we lose, we might perish.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （そうだ・・この戦いの結果で我々は全員死ぬかもしれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (That's right... depending on the outcome of this battle, we might all die.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だからこそ、私は都市長としてジフテリアを守らねばいけないのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's why, as the city mayor, I must protect Diphtheria.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たとえ、他国を犠牲にしようと）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if it means sacrificing other nations.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 回想
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Flashback.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コンバート、カチューシャとの密談
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A secret meeting between Convert and Katyusha.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 決戦時に裏切る事でその後、ジフテリアの安全は保証する約束
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A promise guaranteeing Diphtheria's safety after betrayal at the decisive battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 悪いが裏切らせてもらう、頃合いだな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry, but I have to betray you. The time has come.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 副官に指示する、攻撃開始だ、ただ、目標は魔軍では無い、近くのＸＸＸ軍（布陣図見てから決める）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He orders the deputy officer, 'Start the attack. However, the target is not the demon army, but the nearby XXX army (decided after viewing the deployment map).'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんですってと副官が驚くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The deputy officer is surprised, saying, 'What did you say?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 別の副官が止める、都市長閣下も苦渋の決断なのだと、お前も軍人なら従え
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Another deputy officer stops him, saying, 'The city mayor is making a painful decision. If you are a soldier, obey.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・わかりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Understood.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこにランスからの手紙が届く、受け取るビョンホウ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, a letter from Lance arrives; Byonhou receives it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを見て真っ青になる、ま、待て裏切り中止
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing it, he turns pale. 'W-wait, cancel the betrayal!'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すぐに魔軍に向けて進撃せよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Advance immediately towards the demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍司令部
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon army headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦通りにならずに驚く、大将軍ピサロ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Great General Pizarro is surprised that the plan is not going as expected.
